Description: Fix CVE-2023-32313 - Inspect method should be readonly
 vm2 vulnerable to Inspect Manipulation - attackers could get a
 read-write reference to the node inspect method and edit options
 for console.log, enabling defense evasion within the sandbox.
 This patch makes the inspect method readonly to prevent tampering.
Origin: upstream, https://github.com/patriksimek/vm2/commit/5206ba25afd86ef547a2c9d48d46ca7a9e6ec238
Author: XmiliaH <xmilia.hermit@gmail.com>
Last-Update: 2023-05-15

