 		if (sandbox) {
 			this.setGlobals(sandbox);

Fix CVE-2023-32314: Ensure host array does not leak through proxy

This patch addresses a sandbox escape vulnerability in vm2 that allows
remote code execution via Proxy specification abuse. The fix adds
sanitization for Proxy handler arguments to prevent host array leakage.

Origin: upstream, https://github.com/patriksimek/vm2/commit/d88105f99752305c5b8a77b63ddee3ec86912daf

